text: Terry L. McMillan is a former American football player and coach. He served as the head football coach at Mississippi College from 1991 to 1999, compiling a record of 45–42–5. McMillan played college football at the University of Southern Mississippi, where he lettered four times as a quarterback. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:American football quarterbacks Category:Mississippi College Choctaws football coaches Category:Southern Miss Golden Eagles football players Category:High school football coaches in Mississippi
